Véra Clouzot https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/V%C3%A9ra_Clouzot 0 Véra Clouzot (30 December 1913 – 15 December 1960) was a Brazilian-French film actress and screenwriter. She is known for playing Christina Delassalle in Les Diaboliques (1955). Véra_Clouzot ( 30_December_1913 – 15_December_1960 ) was a_Brazilian-French_film_actress_and_screenwriter .
